8f0d7e65-0c48-4fcc-8931-29f69d635269.title: <player>
8f0d7e65-0c48-4fcc-8931-29f69d635269.text: Do you know of anything I can do in Morytania?

8ab31b72-7400-4dc9-bc4a-58ae5ffe430b.title: Drezel
8ab31b72-7400-4dc9-bc4a-58ae5ffe430b.text:
Well, not a great deal... but there is something you
could do for me if you're interested. Though it is quite
dangerous.

options.text: Well, what is it, I may be able to help?

66c52d30-34ec-41b8-911f-876a6ea40b2b.title: Drezel
66c52d30-34ec-41b8-911f-876a6ea40b2b.text: Well, I understand. You must be busy.

573c0b55-a064-43c2-b20f-94c4c958f34e.title: <player>
573c0b55-a064-43c2-b20f-94c4c958f34e.text: Well, what is it, I may be able to help?

29101b66-efa2-42c5-80ad-8415d5fd1de6.title: Drezel
29101b66-efa2-42c5-80ad-8415d5fd1de6.text:
There's a man called Filliman who lives in Mort Myre.
He comes by the temple from time to time but I
haven't seen him recently. I was wondering if you
could check in on him?

2b72407f-7047-4975-9487-bfeaab08b5da.title: Drezel
2b72407f-7047-4975-9487-bfeaab08b5da.text:
I must warn you, it could be dangerous. Mort Myre is
filled with ghasts!

011b6eb2-03f8-47cd-899a-744c7c7c87af.title: <player>
011b6eb2-03f8-47cd-899a-744c7c7c87af.text: Sorry, I don't think I can help.

eb319723-d2fa-4e45-ad6b-a0869c5c13a9.title: Drezel
eb319723-d2fa-4e45-ad6b-a0869c5c13a9.text:
That's fine, I'm sure someone else will be along shortly
who can. Now, if you will excuse me, I do have some
things to be getting on with.

74dfa16a-563b-44da-938b-5c74593ad817.title: <player>
74dfa16a-563b-44da-938b-5c74593ad817.text: Yes, I'll go and look for him.

e5151650-3918-4da6-beb3-7d541b42ec8b.title: Drezel
e5151650-3918-4da6-beb3-7d541b42ec8b.text:
Now, please be aware of the ghasts, you cannot attack
them, only Filliman knew how to take them on. Just
run from them if you can. If you get lost, try to make
your way back to the temple.

7c982ca2-e4df-4459-9d78-2f69b68797e1.title: Drezel
7c982ca2-e4df-4459-9d78-2f69b68797e1.text:
Please take this food to Filliman, he'll likely appreciate it.
His home is somewhere in the southern end of Mort
Myre. I don't know the exact location I'm afraid.

9d8bcfe7-b703-464c-a925-677fd982d991.title: <player>
9d8bcfe7-b703-464c-a925-677fd982d991.text:
Don't worry, if he's there and he's still alive, I'll find
him.

7c479c5a-8601-45da-bbd4-865aa4f9587d.title: Drezel
7c479c5a-8601-45da-bbd4-865aa4f9587d.text:
Filliman Tarlock is his full name and he's a druid. He
lives in Mort Myre much like a hermit, but there's
many a traveller who he's helped.

aee94531-37f5-463f-880a-62c6259eff90.title: Drezel
aee94531-37f5-463f-880a-62c6259eff90.text:
Most people that come this way tell stories of when they
were lost and paths that just seemed to 'open up' before
them! I think it was Filliman Tarlock helping out.

7695f37e-547a-4fa7-9d0e-a069c1eb0468.title: Drezel
7695f37e-547a-4fa7-9d0e-a069c1eb0468.text:
Mort Myre is a decayed and dangerous swamp to the
south east of here. Legend says it was once a beautiful
forest called Humblethorn. Now, it's filled with vile
emanations from within Morytania.

b9dd086b-ddfb-460b-a9d0-c1585b382be7.title: Drezel
b9dd086b-ddfb-460b-a9d0-c1585b382be7.text:
The swamp decays everything. We put a fence around
it to stop unwary travellers going in. Anyone who dies
in the swamp is forever cursed to haunt it as a ghast.

ae46c6c6-877a-4021-9857-a3dda10b14ab.title: Drezel
ae46c6c6-877a-4021-9857-a3dda10b14ab.text: Ghasts attack travellers, turning food to rotten filth.

bdfc6bf1-03b3-4a8f-850a-ed451db1777a.title: Drezel
bdfc6bf1-03b3-4a8f-850a-ed451db1777a.text:
A Ghast is a poor soul who died in Mort Myre.
They're undead of a special class and they're
untouchable as far as I'm aware! Filliman knows how to
tackle them though.

186a1436-3ee6-4b27-80ba-e1680e50d093.title: Drezel
186a1436-3ee6-4b27-80ba-e1680e50d093.text:
When they attack, ghasts will devour any food you
have. If you have no food, they'll draw their
nourishment from you!

8e4bdbc6-7181-4173-8544-7a672fe3ecd0.title: Drezel
8e4bdbc6-7181-4173-8544-7a672fe3ecd0.text: Have you managed to find Filliman yet?

e28d4e55-d6be-49a0-b538-119424e20a42.title: Drezel
e28d4e55-d6be-49a0-b538-119424e20a42.text: Please go and look for him, I would appreciate it!

options.text: Where should I look for Filliman Tarlock again?
Explain to me what a Ghast is again.
What's the story with Mort Myre?
What's the story with Filliman Tarlock?

b5eeb29c-3d5f-49dd-925c-4036bf2cf7ac.title: <player>
b5eeb29c-3d5f-49dd-925c-4036bf2cf7ac.text: Where should I look for Filliman Tarlock again?

7dad83d3-fe73-42ad-96cd-471efe8ebcdc.title: Drezel
7dad83d3-fe73-42ad-96cd-471efe8ebcdc.text:
Search to the south of Mort Myre. Remember that he's
a druid so he can conceal himself within nature quite
well. My guess is that he lives in the southern area of
the swamp, though he could be anywhere.

e1f1650d-2de8-4a6a-b217-f5d692174502.title: <player>
e1f1650d-2de8-4a6a-b217-f5d692174502.text: Explain to me what a Ghast is again.

d6e2947b-3827-4da3-a344-08871993a7e9.title: Drezel
d6e2947b-3827-4da3-a344-08871993a7e9.text:
A Ghast is a poor soul who died in Mort Myre.
They're undead of a special class, they're untouchable
apart from with special druidic items.

ba3e01c1-9424-44cd-ad6d-36ad2ef842f0.title: Drezel
ba3e01c1-9424-44cd-ad6d-36ad2ef842f0.text:
Filliman knew how to tackle them, but I've not heard
from him in a long time. Ghasts, when they attack, will
devour any food you have. If you have no food, they'll
draw their nourishment from you!

f69ca9c2-4fd0-499f-93b3-d2f99f087b17.title: <player>
f69ca9c2-4fd0-499f-93b3-d2f99f087b17.text: What's the story with Mort Myre?

985315ab-836b-4df7-b1ce-d3cbc907e01f.title: Drezel
985315ab-836b-4df7-b1ce-d3cbc907e01f.text:
Mort Myre was once a beautiful forest by the name of
Humblethorn until the evil denizens of Morytania
descended. Now their evil emanations have putrified and
diseased the forest into a decaying swamp of death.

dd6933fa-8ba1-457e-9fd8-7471660f97a3.title: <player>
dd6933fa-8ba1-457e-9fd8-7471660f97a3.text: What's the story with Filliman Tarlock?

10142d47-c91a-46c8-905f-e20afb000281.title: Drezel
10142d47-c91a-46c8-905f-e20afb000281.text:
Filliman is a druid of some considerable power. He
helped many people in Morytania escape when the evil
descended upon the land. His knowledge of plants and
nature was exceptional.

da7b51ce-c1bb-4292-94bf-05ca7befa1dd.title: Drezel
da7b51ce-c1bb-4292-94bf-05ca7befa1dd.text:
But one day, he was betrayed by some of the people
who he had tried to help. This naturally made him more
careful when dealing with strangers again and so,
instead of showing himself, he would follow them.

9baee7ad-e1e2-4d60-9076-6eb7ee5461a0.title: Drezel
9baee7ad-e1e2-4d60-9076-6eb7ee5461a0.text:
He would follow them at a distance and make the path
clear for them, showing them to the temple and to
salvation. Saradomin bless him! He is a good man.

47f7d1a4-3467-4e42-8055-3fc150dd7244.title: Drezel
47f7d1a4-3467-4e42-8055-3fc150dd7244.text:
He was always losing things in his camp, take a good
look around.

a79fc705-0d7a-483e-a954-d6d190b3077b.title: <player>
a79fc705-0d7a-483e-a954-d6d190b3077b.text:
Hello again! I'm helping Filliman, he plans to become a
nature spirit. I have a spell to cast but first I need to
be blessed. Can you bless me?

07f8b82d-a293-4988-a519-1d2b4bce44f8.title: Drezel
07f8b82d-a293-4988-a519-1d2b4bce44f8.text:
Very well my friend, prepare yourself for the blessings
of Saradomin. Here we go!

afd0faf1-564e-4d10-bd52-4c24674b7a94.title: Drezel
afd0faf1-564e-4d10-bd52-4c24674b7a94.text:
There you go my friend, you're now blessed. It's
funny, now I look at you, there seems to be something
of the faith about you. Anyway, good luck with your
quest!

e7e56b78-ffe1-485e-90eb-df2d2500be2b.title: Drezel
e7e56b78-ffe1-485e-90eb-df2d2500be2b.text: How's life been treating you since you got blessed?

8d479aba-a3f6-4235-ad6a-f6b169afa096.title: Drezel
8d479aba-a3f6-4235-ad6a-f6b169afa096.text:
It's funny, because when I look at you, there does
seem to be something of the faith about you. Have you
considered a life of service to Saradomin?

d0d6b46a-6724-492d-a747-a64b5a6c6f4b.title: <player>
d0d6b46a-6724-492d-a747-a64b5a6c6f4b.text: I serve Saradomin in other ways.

4f0cfa3b-b624-47ab-9cab-0ab60700d0e8.title: <player>
4f0cfa3b-b624-47ab-9cab-0ab60700d0e8.text:
I've picked the Fungus, but I'm not sure what to do
now.

6d70c8e6-4252-4fb1-b378-df433e272990.title: Drezel
6d70c8e6-4252-4fb1-b378-df433e272990.text:
Well, perhaps Filliman needs it? Why not show it to
him.

74499e84-ce7a-44f6-b4ef-24254e4662bc.title: <player>
74499e84-ce7a-44f6-b4ef-24254e4662bc.text:
I've placed all the items and Filliman said that spell was
cast. What do I do now?

54c5fef2-4bbe-4aef-95d8-57fb28b73f70.title: Drezel
54c5fef2-4bbe-4aef-95d8-57fb28b73f70.text:
Where did he go to? Why not ask him for some help.
Perhaps he went into his grotto.

d14f66c3-88a1-4e8e-9ebf-15d195124bb1.title: <player>
d14f66c3-88a1-4e8e-9ebf-15d195124bb1.text:
Hi again. Filliman has turned into the Nature Spirit.
I've just gotten the Silver sickle that he asked me to
get. He says he's going to bless it!

3ca81fa3-19b4-4ff8-9af0-c3b3919d7751.title: Drezel
3ca81fa3-19b4-4ff8-9af0-c3b3919d7751.text:
Well, that's great! You'd best take it to him then with all
haste!

09cd5a78-5361-4bdd-b7be-9159009a929f.title: <player>
09cd5a78-5361-4bdd-b7be-9159009a929f.text:
Hi again. Filliman has turned into the Nature Spirit. I
now need to get a silver sickle so that I can try and
defeat the Ghasts. Do you know where I could get
something like that?

6573217d-ab66-4560-b1f6-0b54ad2eb38e.title: Drezel
6573217d-ab66-4560-b1f6-0b54ad2eb38e.text:
Well, let me think now. Aha, yes, if you're making
something from silver, you'll more than likely need a
mould, most crafting shops sell them, you could get one
from Al Kharid.

8f1a6807-c1df-4128-aece-6bd202cb8dac.title: Drezel
8f1a6807-c1df-4128-aece-6bd202cb8dac.text:
You can mine silver from a silver rock, you can find
some on the way to Al Kharid.

36436b38-1937-40a7-8c09-152f3fd8996d.title: <player>
36436b38-1937-40a7-8c09-152f3fd8996d.text:
Hey there, Filliman blessed my silver sickle, but now
I've got to kill three Ghasts, but I'm not sure how to
make them appear.

7d94fd1b-a8e3-41b9-b034-fca8253c47e6.title: Drezel
7d94fd1b-a8e3-41b9-b034-fca8253c47e6.text:
Well, did Filliman give you any special instructions on
how to combat them?

ffc4395f-f599-4cbb-86ef-0e5d5d0d0da4.title: <player>
ffc4395f-f599-4cbb-86ef-0e5d5d0d0da4.text:
Only something about harvesting natures bounty...
that's all!

fb9d3f90-c4fa-4577-b3e9-8e588297a409.title: Drezel
fb9d3f90-c4fa-4577-b3e9-8e588297a409.text:
Well, perhaps it has something to do with the silver
sickle, do you think that in blessing it, it did something
special to it?

b16f662d-b11d-4faf-b527-2730e33d84a9.title: Note
b16f662d-b11d-4faf-b527-2730e33d84a9.text: Missing dialogue if you have added to the pouch but not killed any ghasts

0cb3206f-5823-45cf-9c45-10efcb4578f8.title: <player>
0cb3206f-5823-45cf-9c45-10efcb4578f8.text: Hiya, I'm a mighty Ghast killer! I've killed <nature_spirit_ghast_kills> so far!

d1718a8c-3dd6-4ef4-9cd9-cae4f4d64a0e.title: Drezel
d1718a8c-3dd6-4ef4-9cd9-cae4f4d64a0e.text: That's great! How many did Filliman ask you kill?

91ace9d1-75ad-4cfe-86bb-bf207e39088f.title: Drezel
91ace9d1-75ad-4cfe-86bb-bf207e39088f.text: So, you've got <nature_spirit_ghast_remaining> more to kill then!

644b1df3-8729-4564-9a16-38abc0b91f3e.title: Drezel
644b1df3-8729-4564-9a16-38abc0b91f3e.text:
So, you've killed them all then! Go and tell him, I'll bet
he'll be pleased.

48c17814-d525-4ee4-a021-b6034c17083b.title: <player>
48c17814-d525-4ee4-a021-b6034c17083b.text: Hi there! Filliman says I've completed the quest!

dbc30dd9-4fe3-4730-a76e-34e7ab6d2b59.title: Drezel
dbc30dd9-4fe3-4730-a76e-34e7ab6d2b59.text:
Ah, <player>. Glad you made it. Things are worse
than I feared down here. I'm not sure if I will be able
to repair the damage.

ff9aa2eb-7cfc-4931-bb01-fc642a6c4e42.title: Drezel
ff9aa2eb-7cfc-4931-bb01-fc642a6c4e42.text:
Sadly, with the guard dog gone, there was nothing to
stop those Zamorakians from entering the mausoleum.
From what I can tell, they have used some kind of evil
potion to pollute the Salve.

693cd7c0-5239-4ca1-b65b-fa049340d116.title: Drezel
693cd7c0-5239-4ca1-b65b-fa049340d116.text:
The well here is built right over the source of the river.
That means that their potion will spread all the way
down the Salve, disrupting the blessings placed upon it.

dd95da61-2222-46c5-bf49-8e7d3eb04fbf.title: Drezel
dd95da61-2222-46c5-bf49-8e7d3eb04fbf.text:
Before long, there will be nothing to stop the vampyres
from invading Misthalin at their leisure.

030323f3-fb93-431c-8d28-7935a10e4cde.title: <player>
030323f3-fb93-431c-8d28-7935a10e4cde.text: What can we do to prevent that?

732830d9-dbbd-4a4d-ac1d-2fafb3bdf908.title: Drezel
732830d9-dbbd-4a4d-ac1d-2fafb3bdf908.text:
This passage is currently the only route between
Morytania and Misthalin. The barrier here draws power
from the river.

69145784-4920-4ac9-a676-bc726ae8f076.title: Drezel
69145784-4920-4ac9-a676-bc726ae8f076.text:
I have managed to reinforce the barrier, but I must
continue focussing on it to keep it intact. Although the
passage is safe for now, I do not know how long I can
keep it that way.

50547d59-841d-42a4-bc85-c35ef72d552a.title: Drezel
50547d59-841d-42a4-bc85-c35ef72d552a.text:
This passage could be the least of our worries soon
though. Before long, the vampyres will be able to cross
at any point of the river. We won't be able to reinforce
all of it.

3968a0e9-b35b-46eb-bcc8-4b18c83ecfa3.title: <player>
3968a0e9-b35b-46eb-bcc8-4b18c83ecfa3.text:
Couldn't you bless the river to purify it? Like you did
with the water I took from the well?

913981a3-52a1-4edf-9995-0b7d062f8e8b.title: Drezel
913981a3-52a1-4edf-9995-0b7d062f8e8b.text:
No, that would not work. The power I have from
Saradomin is not great enough to cleanse an entire
river of this foul Zamorakian pollutant.

19b8aeff-ea2c-4bcf-9c3f-68551045f98c.title: Drezel
19b8aeff-ea2c-4bcf-9c3f-68551045f98c.text: However, I do have one other idea.

58a0250e-7b02-4504-9073-792b6c108a64.title: Drezel
58a0250e-7b02-4504-9073-792b6c108a64.text:
I believe we might be able to soak up the evil magic that
the potion has released into the river.

e3fa5127-da53-45fd-8031-b1115b1f02d8.title: Drezel
e3fa5127-da53-45fd-8031-b1115b1f02d8.text:
I'm sure you know of runestones, used by mages to
power their spells. The essence used to create these
stones absorbs magical potential from runic altars to be
released later.

44b304d2-1bfc-4565-9a74-810180e45d42.title: <player>
44b304d2-1bfc-4565-9a74-810180e45d42.text:
And you think we could use some rune essence to
absorb the magic they've released into the Salve?

595f06e0-a61e-4478-90c5-1b8576172fc5.title: Drezel
595f06e0-a61e-4478-90c5-1b8576172fc5.text:
Exactly. If you could bring me fifty essence, I should
be able to reverse the damage done. Be quick though.
The longer we wait, the worse things will get.

3bb03937-5974-45d2-b875-8fea21082c1b.title: Drezel
3bb03937-5974-45d2-b875-8fea21082c1b.text:
Excellent! That should do it! I will bless these stones
and place them within the well. With the river safe,
Misthalin should be protected from the vampyres once
more!

1ae594da-6669-4721-b293-34324f41e42b.title: Drezel
1ae594da-6669-4721-b293-34324f41e42b.text:
Please take this dagger. It has been handed down within
my family for generations and is filled with the power of
Saradomin.

b300a87b-1773-4160-8dad-a8264a8a3c41.title: Drezel
b300a87b-1773-4160-8dad-a8264a8a3c41.text:
You will find that it has the ability to prevent
werewolves from adopting their wolf form in combat.
Hopefully it comes in useful.
